data.description: **10,000 CREDIT OFFERED BY SELLER!!* TO BE USED FOR RATE BUY DOWN OR OTHERWISE**!!! Immediately notice the expansive mountain views and covered front porch with beautiful neutral finishes inside and out! Enter the front door and experience warmth, natural sunlight, and the feeling of a new home throughout. You will be greeted with a large entry way, 9' ceilings, LVP flooring, two good-sized bedrooms with large windows and a shared full bathroom. As you continue through the home, you will be greeted with an incredible open floor plan, stunning kitchen with huge pantry, gas stove, island, and stainless-steel appliances. The primary bedroom in the back of the home provides privacy, a beautiful ensuite bathroom and large walk-in closet. Make your way to the backyard where there is an incredible raised, stamped concrete patio with enclosed privacy fencing and open space with walking/bike trail behind the home. Included is a gigantic 3-car garage, large laundry room with washer, dryer and extra refrigerator, energy efficient tankless hot water heater, smart home possibility and brand-new roof. Quick access to I-25 and just minutes from shopping, dining, and entertainment in downtown Frederick!
